CentreonBroker is a Nagios Event Broker Module that can export monitoring
events to a database. It has the following features :

 - configurable log output
 - multi instance input
 - multi socket input
 - multi output
 - TLS on connections possible
 - lower network footprint
 - smaller DB load
 - optimized DB schema
 - written in C++ for more stability
 - fully configurable
 - multi-threaded (make use of modern processors)
